## Compact Instructions

When compacting conversation history, always preserve:
- Current InProgress task ID, title, and full acceptance criteria
- Blocked status with specific blocking reasons and blocked_by task IDs
- Pending Change Requests (CR number, status, and proposed changes)
- Current session's uncommitted work and verification results

